Definition: a later sacred text of Hinduism of a mystical nature dealing with metaphysical questions
Example: the Vedanta philosophy developed from the pantheistic views of the Upanishads
Synonyms: sacred_text, i, a, later, sacred, text, of, Hinduism, mystical, nature, dealing, with, metaphysical, questions, the, Vedanta, philosophy, developed, from, pantheistic, views, Upanishads
Category: noun.communication
